          "itemName": "Multi-Optical System",
          "sdc": 20,
          "regenerationRule": "per_24_hours",
          "effectFormula": "Laser rangefinder and 2 mi (3.2 km) telescopic zoom; passive nightvision, IR, and UV 1,000 ft (305 m); macro 20×; auto-tint vs sudden flashes."
