          "itemName": "Rocket Jump Boots",
          "sdc": 20,
          "regenerationRule": "per_24_hours",
          "effectFormula": "Leap 50 ft (15.2 m) high or 12 ft (3.7 m) high and 100 ft (30.5 m) across; safe land from 200 ft (61 m), half damage higher. Rocket leap kick/body block: 2 attacks, +10 damage, 01-50% knockdown human-sized."
        },
        {
          "id": "gadget_stun_bola",
          "itemName": "Stun Bola",
          "sdc": 20,
          "usageLimit": 3,
          "regenerationRule": "per_24_hours",
          "effectFormula": "Thrown/fired bola -2 disarm (called shot); save 13+ or stunned (-2 attacks, -3 combat 1D4 rounds); roll 5- or dazed 1D4 rounds. Untangle 1D4+2 actions or S.P.S. 30+ or 30 S.D.C. to cut free.",
          "traitFlags": ["auto_returning"]
        }
      ],
      "customOneOffs": [
        "Gadgets are part of the Morphus and work only for this Nightbane; each has 20 S.D.C. unless noted.",
